    "date": "2022-10-11T11:01:32Z",
    "text": "Military Threat Awareness Act of 2022\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Defense (DOD) to make publicly available reports on the military capabilities of China, Iran, North Korea, and Russia. Each report must be made available in unclassified form on a publicly accessible DOD website.\n\nDOD may use or add to any existing reports to respond to the reporting requirement."
